item.description:
Castro is an information utility for your tablets and smartphones. It displays various diagnostic information about the device. Castro processes and displays a huge amount of information, namely
	Detailed processor statistics (CPU and GPU);
	Battery monitoring;
	Consumes all types of memory;
	Data usage over Wi-Fi and mobile networks;
	Real-time sensor data with helpful graphs;
	Detailed information about the device's camera;
	Full list of available audio and video codecs;
